parsedComplaintsResult.impact: Water infiltration can cause electrical issues, including audible alarms, and potentially lead to driver distraction, accidents, or electrical system failures.

parsedComplaintsResult.issueCategory: Brake Pedal Failure and Sudden Loss of Braking Power
parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the brake pedal can cause a sudden loss of braking power, leading to accidents or near-misses.
